ariko tukinjira cyane mu isesengura ry'isoko

26
00:01:29,853 --> 00:01:34,353
kubera ko byinshi mu byemezo
mwafashe kugeza ubu ni iby'ibanze.

27
00:01:34,964 --> 00:01:36,930
Mwabishingiye ku bitekerezo,

28
