uburyo ushobora
gukora igenzura ry'isoko,

38
00:02:07,910 --> 00:02:12,180
ariko tugasoza kano gace
tureba inzira uzanyuramo kugirango utere imbere mu gihe kizaza,

39
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:14,507
kubera ko amahirwe werekanye

40
00:02:14,507 --> 00:02:17,193
aguha imishobokere idasanzwe
yo gutera imbere nyuma yigihe,

41
00:02:17,220 --> 00:02:20,215
bivuze ko ushobora kunyuranya
muri utu duce tundi

42
