wakoze cyane kuri icyo gikorwa.

77
00:04:17,007 --> 00:04:19,511
Ariko hari ingorane,
bisa n'umutego,

78
00:04:19,511 --> 00:04:22,793
kubera ko ushaka gusobanukirwa neza
igitekerezo cy'abakiliya,

79
00:04:22,793 --> 00:04:25,825
ukeneye gusobanukirwa igitekerezo cy'abakiliya
kugira ngo ubashe kugurisha.

80
00:04:25,825 --> 00:04:28,098
Kandi niwishyira
mu mwanya w'abakiliya,

81
