93
00:05:10,949 --> 00:05:13,620
ariko igitekerezo cyabo ni ikingenzi
mu kugurisha.

94
00:05:13,620 --> 00:05:15,742
Kubera iyo mpamvu ni ayahe makuru
ukeneye kubona

95
00:05:15,742 --> 00:05:16,842
kugirango usobanukirwe

96
