riguha ahantu heza
watangirira umurimo?

98
00:05:24,372 --> 00:05:26,601
Hari ibibazo by'ingenzi
bisabwa gusubizwa,

99
00:05:26,601 --> 00:05:31,527
kandi mu by'ukuri, abantu bamwe, cyane cyane
iyo uri rwiyemezamirimo mu ikoranabuhanga,

100
00:05:31,527 --> 00:05:34,111
ushobora gukora kugahato
cyangwa se ushobora kutabyishimiramo cyane

101
00:05:34,111 --> 00:05:39,606
kugenda hariya kuvugana n'abakiliya
ukanakusanya amakuru yose.

102
00:05:40,355 --> 00:05:43,783
Ibyo birumvikana
kubera ko utabihuguriwemo.

103
00:05:43,783 --> 00:05:47,028
Ariko kurundi ruhande,
reba kuri iri gerageza rindi.

104
00:05:47,028 --> 00:05:50,952
Genda hariya, ugende
uvugane n'abantu batandukanye,

105
00:05:50,952 --> 00:05:52,635
kandi ukusanye amakuru

106
00:05:52,636 --> 00:05:55,122
--nzakwereka
izindi nzira nyuma--

107
00:05:55,123 --> 00:05:57,855
ariko aka mu by'ukuri ni
agatego gasaba ubwenge.

108
00:05:57,954 --> 00:06:03,648
bivuze ko, igikorwa, intumbero
mfitiye isoko ryanjye mu by'ukuri niryo?

109
00:06:04,328 --> 00:06:07,886
Iri ni nkigenzura cyangwa se igerageza ritoya
ushobora gukora muri labaratwari yawe.

110
00:06:08,035 --> 00:06:11,438
Bityo ni ibihe bibazo by'ingenzi 
ushobora kuba washubije?

111
00:06:12,212 --> 00:06:15,686
Ni ibihe bibazo byagufasha
kunoza igitekerezo cyawe?

112
00:06:15,771 --> 00:06:17,750
Icyambere ntagushidikanya, ni ugukenera.

113
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:20,404
amakuru ajyanye no gukenera,
ni kuruhe rugero bakeneye.

114
00:06:20,404 --> 00:06:24,901
Wibuke iri jambo ryiza," ububabare bw'umukiliya"
twaganiriye ubushize.

115
00:06:25,422 --> 00:06:27,612
Gukenera nabyo bifite ishami ry'ingano,

116
00:06:27,612 --> 00:06:30,353
ni abakiliya bangahe
bafite ubwo bubabare hariya hanze?

117
00:06:30,782 --> 00:06:34,137
Mu yandi magambo,
hari ubwo ufite ahantu heza

118
00:06:34,137 --> 00:06:37,531
hanini hahagije ho gufasha
gutangiza umurimo watera imbere vuba?

119
00:06:38,397 --> 00:06:41,213
Icya kabiri, wakenera
gusobanukirwa ihangana,

120
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:44,244
kandi n'ikibazo kimwe kiri
by'umwihariko ku mugambe mubisha bwambere

121
00:06:44,244 --> 00:06:46,885
ni ikibazo cya ni ubuhe bwoko bwibikorwa

122
00:06:46,885 --> 00:06:50,401
Hari ubwo abakiliya bawe bagereranya
impano zawe ku?

123
00:06:50,857 --> 00:06:53,744
Ubu bwoko bw'ikibazo
mu by'ukuri bugufusha gusobanukirwa

124
00:06:53,766 --> 00:06:57,844
ikintu kidasanzwe ku gikorwa cyawe
mu maso y'abakiliya bawe,

125
00:06:57,930 --> 00:06:59,637
atari mu maso yawe.

126
00:06:59,749 --> 00:07:01,832
Nanone bigufasha gusobanukirwa

127
00:07:01,832 --> 00:07:07,001
ni ubuhe bwoko bw'ibikorwa bishobora
kugutsinda.

128
00:07:08,025 --> 00:07:10,695
kandi ahari ushobora gutuma
igikorwa cyawe kiba ikidasanzwe.

129
00:07:10,918 --> 00:07:12,913
Ibyo bituzana ku igingo ya gatatu,

130
00:07:13,437 --> 00:07:15,882
Ni ibiki abakiliya batekereza 
ku mpano zawe?

131
00:07:15,882 --> 00:07:18,096
cyerekeranye n'impano zihatana?

132
00:07:18,096 --> 00:07:20,192
Ni iki gituma impano zawe zitandukana n'izindi?

133
00:07:20,340 --> 00:07:22,420
Iki mu by'ukuri ni ikibazo cy'ingenzi

134
