bitamenyerewe kandi bihendutse.

135
00:07:30,075 --> 00:07:33,294
Bityo, muri ubwo buryo ukeneye gusobanukirwa

136
00:07:33,295 --> 00:07:36,898
niba impano yawe
ifite ahantu hahatana kuri yo.

137
00:07:38,081 --> 00:07:41,057
Umukiliya ashobora no kuguha
amakuru y'uburyo

138
00:07:41,057 --> 00:07:43,517
wanoze akurusho kawe

139
00:07:43,517 --> 00:07:46,846
ibyo biguha cyane bikomeye
gahunda idasanzwe yo gucuruza.

140
00:07:47,157 --> 00:07:51,861
Ukeneye no gusobanukirwa agaciro
k'igicuruzwa cyawe cyongerera abakiliya. 

141
00:07:52,243 --> 00:07:56,150
Wibuke ko ubushize twabiganiriyeho
gato, ubwo twavugaga,"ntacyo, ukeneye

142
00:07:56,151 --> 00:07:59,546
gusobanukirwa no gupima
inyungu y'umukiliya."

143
00:08:01,105 --> 00:08:04,113
Ukeneye gusobanukirwa
uko wagera ku bakiliya,

144
00:08:04,114 --> 00:08:06,162
ni hehe umukiliya yagurira igicuruzwa.

145
00:08:06,162 --> 00:08:08,577
Ushobora kuba ufite ibitekerezo
ariko hashobora kuba hari indi miyoboro

146
00:08:08,577 --> 00:08:12,572
aho umukiliya agurira
ibicuruzwa byubwoko nkubwo

147
00:08:12,632 --> 00:08:14,784
urimo kugerageza gucuruza cyane.

148
00:08:14,784 --> 00:08:19,003
Igihera, ukeneye no gusobanukirwa
ni ibihe bikoresho byo kwamamaza byakora neza.

149
00:08:19,003 --> 00:08:21,777
Hari n'izindi ngingo, nanone:
amategeko abaho,

150
00:08:21,777 --> 00:08:24,343
