ukeneye gusobanukirwa?

151
00:08:24,343 --> 00:08:27,000
bityo rero iyo urebye kuri ibi bibazo byose
bigaragara nkaho ari byinshi.

152
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:30,320
Yego, ariko mu by'ukuri
bikenewe gusobanukirwa

153
00:08:30,458 --> 00:08:34,027
kubera ko biguhereza
amakuru menshi y'ingenzi

154
00:08:34,027 --> 00:08:37,711
mu rugendo rwawe rwo kuba
rwiyemezamirimo mwiza.

155
00:08:37,712 --> 00:08:40,056
Nkuko nabivuze, reba ibi
nkaho ari igerageza risaba ubwenge,

156
00:08:40,057 --> 00:08:43,945
kandi ubirebe nkaho ari ukwishimisha, kubera ko abakiliya
hariya hanze ntago ari bo banzi,

157
00:08:43,945 --> 00:08:46,039
ahubwo n'inshuti zawe,

158
00:08:46,042 --> 00:08:50,668
kandi nibo barimo kukwemerera
gutangiza umurimo wawe,

159
00:08:50,669 --> 00:08:56,400
aribo barimo kuguhindura mu by'ukuri,
rwiyemeza mirimo mwiza, by'amahirwe,

160
