170
00:09:33,036 --> 00:09:35,237
urimo gukora ku miterere
y'igicuruzwa cyawe,

171
00:09:35,237 --> 00:09:37,475
kandi n'ibyingenzi kugerageza gukora

172
00:09:37,475 --> 00:09:41,985
icyo utekereza ko ari impano
umukiliya akunda cyane,

173
00:09:41,986 --> 00:09:44,839
kubera ko umukiliya akeneye
gutekereza ku mpano yawe.

174
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:47,931
Kandi uko umukiliya
arushaho gutekereza ku mpano yawe,

175
