00:10:12,070 --> 00:10:15,004
bityo ushobora kubibona
mu biro by'ibarurishamibare byanyu,

183
00:10:15,004 --> 00:10:17,167
mu bigo bya reta, n'ahandi.

184
00:10:17,442 --> 00:10:20,148
Icyagombwa cyo gusobanukirwa

185
00:10:20,148 --> 00:10:22,720
ni uko ahantu
waba uherereye

186
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:26,796
ushobora kutabona amakuru menshi
ahari ku buryo buhagije.

187
00:10:26,796 --> 00:10:30,099
N'iki wakora mur'iki gihe?

188
00:10:30,100 --> 00:10:33,092
Ushobora kuvuga, "Yego, n'uko
nta kintu kidukikije.

189
00:10:33,093 --> 00:10:34,811
Ndagihagarika."

190
00:10:34,811 --> 00:10:36,652
Ariko mu by'ukuri, ba rwiyemezamirimo beza baravuga,

191
00:10:36,652 --> 00:10:38,851
"Yego, ubanza hari
andi makuru

192
00:10:38,851 --> 00:10:41,144
ibyo bishobora kumfasha gusobanukirwa
isoko ryanjye neza.

193
00:10:41,436 --> 00:10:42,996
Nanone ibi ntago bivuze

194
00:10:42,996 --> 00:10:46,086
ko ngomba kuba mfite amakuru yerekeye
ahantu isoko ryanjye riherereye,"

195
00:10:46,086 --> 00:10:49,697
--mu gihe urimo gufungura
igikorwa cyawe mu gihugu runtaka,

196
00:10:49,698 --> 00:10:51,540
kandi nta
makuru menshi ar'aho--

197
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:53,616
Ushobora kugera mu bihugu bindi.

198
00:10:53,616 --> 00:10:57,507
Ibihugu bimwe bishobora kuba biyoboye
 mu kuzamura ikoranabuhanga ryawe,

199
00:10:57,508 --> 00:11:01,593
hashobora kuba hari
amakuru arenzeho

200
00:11:01,594 --> 00:11:06,176
yerekeranye nibyo abakiliya bashaka, guhindagurika ku masoko,
bityo ushobora mu by'ukuri kwigira

201
00:11:06,177 --> 00:11:09,357
ku handi hantu
ibyerekeranye n'amasoko yawe.

202
00:11:09,358 --> 00:11:12,965
Ntago ari ukudaha agaciro,
nkuko nabivuze, biraguha

203
00:11:12,966 --> 00:11:16,294
byibura amwe
 mu makuru wakoresha.

204
00:11:16,295 --> 00:11:21,608
Ubushakashatsi bukorerwa aho mukorera ntago bwaburizamo
ubundi buryo bw'ubushakashatsi, ubushakashatsi bwo ku mbuga,

205
00:11:21,609 --> 00:11:23,901
kandi tuzagera kur'ibyo mu nzego zizakurikira.

206
00:11:23,902 --> 00:11:26,641
urwego rwa gatatu rw'ingenzi ni
ibijya ku rubuga.

207
00:11:26,642 --> 00:11:31,242
Cyakora atari ku bakiliya,
ahubwo bijya mu bubiko, mu maduka

208
00:11:31,250 --> 00:11:34,944
bijya ahantu hatndukanye hagaragara,

209
00:11:34,945 --> 00:11:41,223
aho ushobora kubona amakuru
urubuga rwawe rwo guhatana.

210
00:11:41,224 --> 00:11:44,206
Tekereza ku impano muhatana
ziri hariya hanze;

211
00:11:44,206 --> 00:11:46,394
ushobora gusobanukirwa ibiciro,

212
00:11:46,395 --> 00:11:49,481
uburyo abo muhatana bamamaza impano zabo,

213
00:11:49,482 --> 00:11:53,662
ubwoko bwo kwamamaza
bushobora gukora neza kurusha ubundi,

214
00:11:53,663 --> 00:11:57,281
witegereze abakiliya ba hazaza mu bubiko.

215
00:11:57,282 --> 00:12:01,290
Ugerageze gusobanukirwa uburyo
guhatana bisakaza ibicuruzwa?

216
00:12:01,291 --> 00:12:03,985
Iyo tuvuga ibijyanye no guhatana,

217
00:12:03,986 --> 00:12:08,835
ibi byumvikana cyane
nkaho ari ya mirimo ihatana bya hafi,

218
00:12:08,835 --> 00:12:11,350
ariko ushobora kugira
gusobanukirwa kwagutse ukavuga,

219
00:12:11,350 --> 00:12:18,953
"Ntacyo, ahari har'ubundi buryo byo gusakaza
bukorwa n'iyindi mirimo mu zindi nganda

220
00:12:19,516 --> 00:12:24,886
bushobora kuba burusha ubwanjye
bwo nkoresha ubu,

221
00:12:24,886 --> 00:12:26,286
mu ruganda rwanjye,"

222
00:12:26,286 --> 00:12:29,800
bityo, mur'ubwo busobanuro, ushobora kwigira
kubundi buryo bwo gusakaza,

223
00:12:29,801 --> 00:12:32,830
ubundi buryo bwo kwamamaza,
ubundi buryo bwo kugena ibiciro,

224
00:12:32,831 --> 00:12:35,984
bitewe no kureba ukarenza
imipaka y'uruganda rwawe.

225
00:12:35,985 --> 00:12:39,156
bityo kujya mu rubuga bivuze, icyambere,

226
00:12:39,157 --> 00:12:42,830
"yego, ndabyumva
guhatana mu ruhande rwanjye,

227
00:12:42,831 --> 00:12:44,821
"ariko nkisubizamo imbaraga

228
00:12:44,834 --> 00:12:49,031
"n'uburyo izindi nganda zikora
ibikorwa bisa n'ibi,

229
00:12:49,032 --> 00:12:52,798
kandi bafata ibyemezo bimwe
nibyo tubona hano."

230
00:12:53,188 --> 00:12:56,028
Nk'urwego rukurikira
gerereranya igiciro bishobora kugutwara.

231
00:12:56,493 --> 00:13:00,313
Mu yandi magambo, n'amafaranga angahe bishobora kugutwara
kugirango ugeze impano yawe ku isoko.

232
00:13:00,314 --> 00:13:05,286
Ntago biragera aho kwitiranywa
no kugena ibiciro by'igicuruzwa cyawe,

233
00:13:05,287 --> 00:13:08,045
iyi ni ingingo itandukanye
dushobora kuvugaho mu rwego rur'imbere.

234
00:13:08,045 --> 00:13:09,791
Reka tugerageze gusobanukirwa,

235
00:13:09,792 --> 00:13:13,911
"N'amafaranga angahe mu by'ukuri mfite
yo gushora kugicuruzwa cyanjye?"

236
00:13:13,912 --> 00:13:16,881
Ukeneye gukora ubushakashatsi
ku biciro by'ibikorwa, urugero,

237
00:13:16,882 --> 00:13:19,481
n'amafaranga angahe
 gukwirakwiza ibyakozwe byatwara,

238
00:13:19,482 --> 00:13:22,463
ibiro byatara angahe,
imishahara yatwara angahe,

239
00:13:22,464 --> 00:13:27,692
kandi wenda, niba utinya ibihombo,
kwibwa, ugomba kubibara nabyo.

240
00:13:28,549 --> 00:13:32,668
Ntiwebagirwe gushyiramo
amfaranga wakoreye mur'icyo kigereranyo

241
00:13:32,669 --> 00:13:35,720
kubera ko ushaka kwihemba
umushahara, nawe.

242
00:13:35,809 --> 00:13:38,126
Ariko izi ngingo zose
ziragusobanurira

243
00:13:38,126 --> 00:13:41,165
"neza, n'amafaranga angahe
ibicuruzwa byanjye byanwara?"

244
00:13:41,166 --> 00:13:43,597
kugeza igihe bigeze kubakiriya,

245
00:13:43,598 --> 00:13:47,522
kand'ibi biguhereza ibimenyetso
niba wakunga nyuma y'igihe.

246
00:13:47,688 --> 00:13:52,011
Nk'urwego rukurikira uzakurikiza
gusobanukirwa kugena ibiciro.

247
00:13:52,012 --> 00:13:55,353
Twanditse hano kuri kariya gace
urwego rw'ubushijo bwawe mu biciro

248
00:13:55,354 --> 00:13:58,260
kandi ubu bushobozi
n'ubwingenze cyane,

249
00:13:58,261 --> 00:14:02,833
kubera ko ugomba kuba ufite igitekerezo
k'ubushobozi bwawe ku biciro,

250
00:14:02,901 --> 00:14:07,076
niba usohotse mu rubuga
mu rwego rukurikira ukavugana n'akiliya.

251
00:14:07,570 --> 00:14:11,566
Bityo ukeneye kuzana
n'igitekerezo gihwitse k'urwego rw'igiciro cyawe,

252
00:14:11,567 --> 00:14:14,123
ariko iki nacyo n'igitekerezo
gishobora guhinduka nyuma y'igihe

253
00:14:14,124 --> 00:14:17,300
igihe umaze kumenya
uko abakiliya babona igicuruzwa cyawe,

254
00:14:17,301 --> 00:14:21,133
ugukenera k'umukiliya
mu buryo bwimbitse.

255
00:14:21,134 --> 00:14:23,235
Kenshi, ba rwiyemezamirimo baravuga,

256
00:14:23,250 --> 00:14:26,625
"Nzakoresha zino nzira
nandtse hano."

257
00:14:26,626 --> 00:14:28,293
Bakora inzira yo kongera igiciro,

258
00:14:28,299 --> 00:14:31,457
bityo bashobora kuvuga,"nongeyeho 10%
kugiciro cy'igicuruzwa cyanjye,

259
00:14:31,458 --> 00:14:33,659
kandi aya niyo bazakigura."

260
00:14:33,660 --> 00:14:36,813
Cyangwa bazavuga,"Nkresha
igiciro cy guhatana,

261
00:14:36,814 --> 00:14:40,203
none nkuyeho 10%
bityo igicuruzwa cyanjye cyakundwa cyane."

262
00:14:40,855 --> 00:14:44,352
Cyangwa bagicishe bugufi,
bivuze ko bagiha igiciro gito

263
00:14:44,353 --> 00:14:49,694
bituma
habaho ibicuruzwa bihendutse,

264
00:14:49,854 --> 00:14:53,495
ariko bivuze yuko ushobora
gusiga amafaranga kumeza gutyo.

265
00:14:53,495 --> 00:14:55,625
Kubera iyo mpamvu kubera iki buno buryo buteye ibibazo?

266
00:14:55,642 --> 00:14:58,993
Buno buryo buteye ibibazo
kubera impamvu zitandukanye,

267
00:14:58,994 --> 00:15:02,422
kandi ntekereza ko impamvu nyamukuru ar'
ukubera ko batajya bibaza

268
00:15:02,423 --> 00:15:05,679
agaciro ubona
kubera impano uha abakiliya.

269
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:08,820
Tekereza kuri ibi bikurikira:
mu nzira yo kongera ibiciro, ushobora kuvuga,

270
00:15:08,821 --> 00:15:12,898
"Iki gicuruzwa gihenzeho 20% kurushaho ayo cyanwaye."

271
00:15:13,997 --> 00:15:17,037
Ariko mu by'ukuri, ukagira
cyane, cyane agaciro ku bakiliya,

272
00:15:17,037 --> 00:15:20,721
bityo umukiliya ashobora kuba ashaka
kwishyura menshi ku gicuruzwa cyawe.

273
00:15:20,949 --> 00:15:22,355
Ibi nanone bisobanuye,

274
00:15:22,356 --> 00:15:27,506
"we, ndasiga amafaranga ku meza.
Umukiliya yakabaye anyishyura menshi."

275
00:15:28,439 --> 00:15:30,594
Cyo kimwe, igiciro cyabo muhatana.

276
00:15:30,594 --> 00:15:33,617
Niba ufite igicuruzwa
kirusha ibindi bicuruzwa,

277
00:15:33,617 --> 00:15:35,552
kuber'iki utagicira menshe?

278
00:15:36,437 --> 00:15:39,562
Kandi cyo kimwe
no kucisha bugufi no gucira make

279
00:15:40,093 --> 00:15:44,044
Mur'ubwo busobanuro, ujye ubitekereza,
hanyuma ubitware mu mutima:

280
00:15:44,044 --> 00:15:47,235
ugerageze gusobanukirwa agaciro
urimo kugira ku bakiliya bawe.

281
00:15:47,235 --> 00:15:49,552
Murundi rwego, urwego rwa 6,

282
00:15:49,553 --> 00:15:51,826
mu by'ukuri uragenda ukagera 
ku bakiliya mu isoko ryawe

283
00:15:52,528 --> 00:15:56,451
Uru n'urwego mu by'ukuri rushimishije,
urwego wakigiramo byinshi.

284
00:15:57,024 --> 00:15:58,664
rurashimishije kubera ko hanyuma uhura

285
00:15:58,664 --> 00:16:01,682
nabo bantu
abakiliya bawe nyabo,

286
00:16:01,910 --> 00:16:04,667
abo bazafasha
gushingwa k'umurimo wawe,

287
00:16:04,780 --> 00:16:06,481
bityo aba n'abantu b'ingirakamaro.

288
00:16:06,928 --> 00:16:10,781
nanone n'igikorwa
gishimishije, cy'ubwenge

289
00:16:10,792 --> 00:16:15,501
kubera ko abakiliya bashobora kwemeza
cyangwa se ntibemeze ibitekerezo byawe.

290
00:16:16,635 --> 00:16:18,913
Nturakare
niba batemeje ibitekerezo byawe;

291
00:16:18,913 --> 00:16:20,807
reba ibi nkaho ar'amahirwe yo kwiga.

292
00:16:20,807 --> 00:16:22,886
Ibi n'ibyingirakamaro kubimenya.

293
00:16:23,022 --> 00:16:25,188
Ibaze iyo umukiliya aguhaye

294
00:16:25,189 --> 00:16:27,135
igisubizo utashakaga
kuri bimwe mu birango by'ibicuruzwa 

295
00:16:27,135 --> 00:16:28,794
bishobora kugutangaza.

296
00:16:28,795 --> 00:16:32,538
Benshi muri mwe by'abatangaza
kubera ko, nkuko twavuze mbere,

297
00:16:32,539 --> 00:16:35,903
uru n'uruhinja rwawe, iki n'ikintu waremye
wakoze mu mezi nadi menze

298
00:16:35,903 --> 00:16:38,231
hanyuma umukiliya akaza
akaguha igisubizo kinyuranye.

299
00:16:38,336 --> 00:16:40,692
Ariko reba uburyo bwo kurenga ibyo.

300
00:16:40,693 --> 00:16:44,595
Ufite ubu amahirwe
yo kwiga akuri imbere,

301
00:16:44,741 --> 00:16:47,002
ushobora guhinduraho ku gicuruzwa cyawe,

302
00:16:47,110 --> 00:16:50,755
kandi ushobora kugira igicuruzwa cyawe cyiza
bijyanye no gushaka k'umukiliya.

303
00:16:51,506 --> 00:16:54,730
Kand'ibi ni byiza ko biba kare
uri mu nzira yo gutangiza umurimo

304
00:16:54,731 --> 00:16:57,597
atari bya bindi wamaze gutakaza
umwanya mwinshi ndetse n'amafaranga menshi

305
00:16:57,598 --> 00:17:00,297
mu kugerageza amahirwe
ugasanga

306
00:17:00,297 --> 00:17:03,345
isoko watekerezaga
ko rihari, ntarihari.

307
00:17:03,713 --> 00:17:07,460
Bityo rero ibwiriza ryiza ry'igikumwe ryaba
ngo mu isoko ryibumbiye hamwe neza

308
00:17:07,474 --> 00:17:11,194
urimo kuvugisha abakiliya 50
urimo ugerageza gukusanya ibisubizo

309
00:17:11,195 --> 00:17:13,592
muri izi mande zose
twavuzeho mbere.

310
00:17:13,592 --> 00:17:16,977
muri B2B,
ushobora gusanga ar'amasosiyete make

311
00:17:16,978 --> 00:17:19,833
kubera ko wasanga hari makeya hariya hanze.

312
00:17:19,834 --> 00:17:22,417
Icyangombwa cyo kumenya hariya

313
00:17:22,419 --> 00:17:27,236
"Nkwiye kubonana nuwo muntu
wikorer'amahitamo yo kugura."

314
00:17:29,064 --> 00:17:33,448
Atari ubonetse wese mu muryango,
ahubwo ninde urimo guhitamo kur'uku kugura?

315
00:17:33,449 --> 00:17:36,078
Ushobora ar'itsinda ry'abantu,

316
00:17:36,079 --> 00:17:37,907
ariko ugerageze gusobanukirwa ugushaka kwabo,

317
00:17:37,918 --> 00:17:40,362
ugerageze gusobanukirwa
ishingiro ryo gufata ibyemezo,

318
00:17:40,363 --> 00:17:43,677
kubera ko bizagufasha kunoza
impano yawe, ibikoresho ukoresha mu kwamamaza,

319
00:17:43,678 --> 00:17:47,282
uburyo wamamazamo
ku gushaka kwa bakiliya.

320
00:17:48,232 --> 00:17:52,552
Bityo, bwanyuma, mu rwego rwa7, ukaza mu rugo
n'amakuru menshi wakusanije.

321
00:17:52,553 --> 00:17:56,208
Wakusanije amakuru aho ukorere,

322
00:17:56,209 --> 00:17:58,731
amakuru ku guhatana ku rubuga,

323
00:17:58,732 --> 00:18:01,758
wakuye amakuru
ku bakiliya nyirizina.

324
00:18:02,293 --> 00:18:04,663
Aya makuru menshi aguha

325
00:18:04,664 --> 00:18:08,540
Itangiriro rifatika
kugirango ufate ibyemezo bifite amakuru.

326
00:18:09,639 --> 00:18:15,209
Ubu bwoko bwa makuru ya gongana n'
ibitekerezo war'ufite mbere maze ukavuga,

327
00:18:15,209 --> 00:18:20,127
"yego, wenda bimwe muri byo bijyanye n'isoko,
n'abakiliya, no gusakaza,

328
00:18:20,128 --> 00:18:22,598
nari mfite mbere, ntago ari byo,

329
00:18:22,598 --> 00:18:24,370
ugakenera guhindura
muri ubu buryo cyangwa ubundi."

330
00:18:24,370 --> 00:18:29,184
Nkuko navuze byerekeye n'agace gaherutse,
aya s'amakuru mabi,

331
00:18:29,185 --> 00:18:31,886
aya n'amahirwe yo kwiga
yo gutera imbere no kunoza,

332
00:18:31,886 --> 00:18:33,640
kuva ku byiza ukagera kubirenzeho.

333
00:18:35,669 --> 00:18:39,759
Wenda ntago ar'amakuru yose
na dosiye zose wakusanije

334
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:41,662
zingana mu kugira akamaro.

335
00:18:41,663 --> 00:18:45,624
Icyingenzi cyambere, ahubwo,
n'ibitekerezo biva ku bakiliya bawe.

336
00:18:45,884 --> 00:18:48,440
Ubyiteho cyane.
Nta mafaranga bitwara habe na mba,

337
00:18:48,441 --> 00:18:52,088
kubera ko aba bantu bazatanga
amafaranga yabo baruhiye

338
00:18:52,088 --> 00:18:53,674
mu kugura ibicuruzwa byawe,

339
00:18:53,674 --> 00:18:57,493
bityo ugomba gusobaukirwa uburyo bemera,
ibyo barutisha ibindi, ibyo badakunda,

340
00:18:57,493 --> 00:18:59,672
n'ibyo bakunda
byerekeye ibicuruzwa muhatana.

341
00:19:00,208 --> 00:19:03,318
Ariko hanyuma,
wirinde pararizi mu gusesengura kwawe.

342
00:19:03,318 --> 00:19:05,783
ushobora gusesengura amakuru yawe cyane

343
00:19:05,784 --> 00:19:09,854
mbere yo kujya ku rubuga
no gushyira ahagaragara igicuruzwa cyawe.

344
00:19:09,855 --> 00:19:11,901
Ntuzigera usobanukirwa uburyo

345
00:19:11,902 --> 00:19:15,108
ihatana rifata igicuruzwa cyawe
keretse winjiye mu isoko.

346
00:19:15,881 --> 00:19:18,866
Bityo hari byinshi ushobora gukora
mu kugerageza isoko ryawe,

347
00:19:19,118 --> 00:19:22,194
ndetse n'amakuru afatika y'abakiliya.

348
00:19:22,431 --> 00:19:24,752
witegure izo nzitizi.

349
00:19:25,368 --> 00:19:29,631
Bityo inzego zirindwi zigomba kuguha
amakuru afatika

350
00:19:29,632 --> 00:19:33,397
ajyanye n'isoko ushaka
wateganirije kugez'ubu igikorwa cyawe.

351
00:19:34,587 --> 00:19:37,807
Ugomba kwibaza ikibazo
kimwe na kiriya

352
00:19:37,808 --> 00:19:39,708
twashyize hariya kuri kariya gace

353
00:19:39,709 --> 00:19:42,404
N'iki isesengura rikubwira
ku isoko wahisemo?

354
00:19:42,405 --> 00:19:46,501
Ese aha niho hantu heza
 ho gutangiza igikorwa cyanjye?

355
00:19:47,668 --> 00:19:51,314
Ese nkeneye guhindura ahandi hantu?

356
00:19:51,568 --> 00:19:54,310
Kandi ibi n'ibyingenzi hano.

357
00:19:55,379 --> 00:19:56,735
Ese har'umugambi B?

358
00:19:57,441 --> 00:19:58,686
Kandi yego, har'umugambi B.

359
00:19:59,125 --> 00:20:02,292
Gusubira ku itangiriro
umurongo ngenderwaho wo gukoresh'amahirwe.

360
00:20:02,904 --> 00:20:05,447
Uyu niwo mugambi B.
ushobora kuvuga,

361
00:20:05,447 --> 00:20:10,983
"Iri gerageza ry'isoko
nakoze ntago rifatika.

362
00:20:11,185 --> 00:20:13,114
ntarihari."

363
00:20:13,154 --> 00:20:15,543
Kandi ibi, nkuko nabivuze, ntago ar'umusaruro mubi,

364
00:20:15,543 --> 00:20:21,040
ni umusaruro wagutwaye
imbaraga, waguhangayikishije, wenda,

365
00:20:21,385 --> 00:20:26,514
ariko, ni byiza kwanga ubu,
mbere yuko byanga byagutwaye ibintu byinshi,

366
00:20:26,515 --> 00:20:30,947
maze ukavuga, "ntakibazo, ndareka iri soko,
ariko ndajya gukora ibindi."

367
00:20:31,462 --> 00:20:35,443
Kandi ahandi hantu h'isoko
ushobora gusanga ar'isoko riraha.

368
00:20:35,758 --> 00:20:37,532
ushobora gusanga ar'umugambi B.

369
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:43,972
Cyangwa, reka--dukore bitandukanye--,
niba iri soko ryari ryiza,

370
00:20:44,641 --> 00:20:50,786
ushobora kuvuga, "yego, mu gice cya 2,
nzaguma ntagushidikanya mur'iri soko,

371
00:20:50,786 --> 00:20:53,853
ariko zinjira no murindi."

372
00:20:54,001 --> 00:20:58,245
Ririya n'iryasoko hano, ryari ibyibanze

373
00:20:58,246 --> 00:21:00,518
ibuye ryo kugenderaho
kugirango ujyere ku rindi soko.

374
00:21:01,726 --> 00:21:07,638
Ibi bugaha bimwe bishimishije
imishobokere yo guter'imbere,

375
00:21:08,018 --> 00:21:11,509
kubera k'iyo utekereje ku gihe,

376
00:21:11,509 --> 00:21:13,638
bishobora kuba imyaka myinshi hano,

377
00:21:13,638 --> 00:21:17,159
hari inkuru ishimishije yo guter'imbere
birebana n'umurimo wawe

378
00:21:17,254 --> 00:21:19,312
ushobora kuba utar'agize,

379
00:21:19,433 --> 00:21:22,517
niba wararebye
ku mahirwe amwe y'isoko.

380
00:21:24,118 --> 00:21:29,808
Kandi hari n'inkuru
yo kugira agaciro hano,

381
00:21:30,077 --> 00:21:34,568
ariko hari nindi nzira ishimishije
yo koroshya ibizazane,

382
00:21:34,639 --> 00:21:36,416
kubera ko nkuko navuze mbere,

383
00:21:36,416 --> 00:21:40,611
niba iri soko hano ridakoze,
dufite umugambi B mu bubiko.

384
00:21:40,859 --> 00:21:42,628
Uyu mugambi B ur'aha.

385
00:21:44,775 --> 00:21:47,722
Bityo, mu yandi magambo, iyo uzamutse

386
00:21:47,723 --> 00:21:51,062
niyi nzira igoranye
yo gutangira umurimo wawe,

387
00:21:51,427 --> 00:21:57,377
uba warateguye uburyo bwo guter'imbere
kandi uba waragabanyije ibizazane byawe

388
00:21:57,377 --> 00:22:00,574
aribyo byiza
ba rwiyemezamirimo bahora bakora.

389
00:22:01,129 --> 00:22:06,309
Kuri ibyo byavuzwe, ufite igerageza
rishimishije imbere yawe,

390
00:22:06,754 --> 00:22:08,859
ibikorwa bishimishije imbere yawe.

391
00:22:09,820 --> 00:22:15,768
Icyo nshaka ko ukora n'ugutekereza
n'ubushishozi kandi buhoro buhoro hirya y'inzego,

392
00:22:15,769 --> 00:22:19,116
hanyuma ugerageze gusobanukirwa
icy'ibi bivuze ku murimo wanjye.

393
00:22:19,344 --> 00:22:21,783
Amahirwe masa nibyo!
tuzabonane ubutaha.
